  "body": "At the moment, the \"network client\" (i.e. the provider and block tracker for a specific network) is constructed in two separate places. The middleware and block tracker are constructed in the dedicated network client module (`createInfuraClient.js` or `createJsonRpcClient.js`), then the middleware is extended further in the network controller.\n\nThis arrangement makes it ambiguous where the network client starts and ends. Having a clear representation of the network client in our codebase is important for simultaneous network support.\n\nWe should refactor the network clients such that the entire network client is setup in a dedicated module, distinct from the network controller.",
